{"tid":1250273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[知識補充] 釐清「三權」","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T04:33:42.000Z","uid":229880,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b1a42d73fd72afbd180b4bc21720dbb3317026","tid":1250273,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"見到大家對於應唔應該圍律政司，我係無意見的。<br />\n<br />\n不過，大家嘅討論內容係對於「三權」理解唔準確。<br />\n<br />\n好多討論內容十分明確，係話唔好搞到「司」，因為要「司法獨立」等等。呢點當然認同。<br />\n<br />\n不過，律政司唔係代表果個「司」呀﹗<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，律政司係指政府三司，係政府入面其中部門，係管法律嘅﹗<br />\n即係<strong>律政司係行政機關</strong>黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />﹗<br />\n<br />\n而大家認同要保護嘅「司」，代表嘅係法庭、法官。<br />\n所以，尋日有人話唔好去金鐘高等法院，係好正璀的。<br />\n<br />\n講返，現時大家4點訴求︰<br />\n當中第2、第3點，處理嘅權力其實係律政司度，<strong>刑事檢控人員可以揀檢控罪名</strong>。<br />\n有關觀點亦可參考早幾天劉進圖所寫嘅文章︰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20190619/s00022/1560918369731/%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%AE%93%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E8%94%93%E5%BB%B6%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E5%8A%89%E9%80%B2%E5%9C%96%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20190619%2Fs00022%2F1560918369731%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25AE%2593%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%2594%2593%25E5%25BB%25B6%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%259C%2596%25EF%25BC%2589&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=a7fb4d5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20190619%2Fs00022%2F1560918369731%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25AE%2593%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%2594%2593%25E5%25BB%25B6%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%259C%2596%25EF%25BC%2589&h=f435ef52\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20190619/s00022/1560918369731/%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%8